{"tid":1452353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劇毒催涙煙，殘留體內，可以影響你一生","createTime":"2019-08-12T00:59:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T02:15:33.000Z","uid":281029,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"167f545d316d76127cdd1b5169cc6428e4adc60a","tid":1452353,"uid":281029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:59:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">老人家和小孩短期內都不宜乘搭地鐵<br />\n<br />\n化學系畢業生 謹以有限文字力量<br />\n提醒各位朋友：<br />\n<br />\n請勿光顧 曾經有催淚彈發射<br />\n的地鐵站內的食物供應商<br />\n大家應該知道地鐵站內商店的閘<br />\n並不能隔絕外面的空氣<br />\n而催淚彈的有害物質 並不能在數天內完全揮發<br />\n<br />\n（先不討論催淚彈是否已過期）<br />\n各位請注意⚠<br />\n<br />\n有做building services 嘅朋友告知：差佬太無知。毒煙一經進入地鐵冷氣系統可能入埋條行車隧道，列車行駛會把氣體帶去其他站，唔係一個站出事咁簡單。你地聽日返工帶定手巾仔，要濕手巾或者帶口罩，有唔對路就掩口，有老人家同小朋友就自己諗下搭唔搭。</span></span>"},{"pid":"10ae299fb0a87f0f73be4e2e3cdeac82519f2d67","tid":1452353,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:20:38.000Z","msg":"戴豬嘴搭地鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4184ddc3c1359efd81f7e393ff601bd90c60cfdb","tid":1452353,"uid":255976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10ae299fb0a87f0f73be4e2e3cdeac82519f2d67","tid":1452353,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:20:38.000Z","msg":"戴豬嘴搭地鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:28:29.000Z","msg":"戴口罩又拉得"},{"pid":"9397f7c439d63ecc57e3bfa1b52186808b192620","tid":1452353,"uid":272119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:29:33.000Z","msg":"搭巴士算"},{"pid":"84c537cfdb134d608b11d4fa66c26842458e3a7d","tid":1452353,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4184ddc3c1359efd81f7e393ff601bd90c60cfdb","tid":1452353,"uid":255976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10ae299fb0a87f0f73be4e2e3cdeac82519f2d67","tid":1452353,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime